column5: Here are a few pic's I have taken in the past two days.  Notice the name on the truck?  Well this "Newf" should have watch where he was going.  Yes, he hit the back of the car...    These two guys came flying down Bay St. yesterday.  One has a powered chair and the trailer person doesn't so he just holds on for the ride.  Nice way to get around if you ask me...
I'll say oddly funny...
That wheelchair pic is gold Jerry...gold.
Too bad it took me so long to get my phone out to get a good pic...
Wheelchair nascar.  Youknow they have to work in pairs or you just can't win.  Drafting-pushing
Shake n bake, baby....shake n bake!
LOL that last post was awesome.  When they wake up in the morning they piss excellence...I just wonder if they assist each other with that as well.
I just missed getting a pic of a guy walking down Bay St in a Banana suit!!!
That would be funny, but if you see a guy walking down the street in a banana hammock please hold off on a pic.
noted and I would be walking away rather fast.
So I go out for a walk at lunch to find Mrs Kelly and Dann helping out a friend.  I don't think you can tell in this pic but it's 30x hotter where they are cause of the gril's
So that's where they're selling their crappie?

Your darn toot'n it was hot ! We were cooking steak,chicken,pulled pork,plainten(fried banana)on the 2 big grills. Behind us was 3 of the propane burners with big pots of rice,vegetables,and spanish beans. Kelly was serving the customers and Anthony( young guy at the far right in the pic) and myself were doing the cooking.
Love the matching aprons Skeets.Do the make them for men too?
Are you kidding me? I would have worn a pink one with rose's on it today, It helped block the heat from the grills.
GBW it a move, or I,ll move ya world.LOL  Thanks for that.
I wonder what tomorrow will bring...
Dang... I thought you got video of the Jamacian Bobsled team coming down Bay St !! Looked at litte gay to me.. not that there was anything wrong with that...  Tomorrow...yah.. tomorrow !
Oh I tried for the video was was too slow on the blackberry...
Now that's funny!!
Almost missed it.. left foot !
Did you notice...There was no flames coming off Skeeters apron?
